  "anchor_regression_note": "OP-16 edge_capture = sum(pnl on WIN anchor days 4/29,5/01,5/04) - sum(max(0,-pnl) on LOSS days 5/05,5/06,5/07). NEGATIVE for every OTM cell -> OTM strikes regress J's edge even when aggregate is positive. The 2 formal-bar clears are aggregate/OOS survivors that FAIL the doctrine anchor gate; reported with true_edge=false, not cherry-picked as wins (anti-pattern 2.10)."
